<view class="page wallet-index-page"><view wx:if="{{a}}" class="notice-bar warning" bindtap="{{b}}"><text class="notice-icon">⚠️</text><text class="notice-text">保证金低于最低要求，线路已对车商隐藏</text><text class="notice-action">去充值 ❯</text></view><view wx:if="{{c}}" class="notice-bar danger" bindtap="{{d}}"><text class="notice-icon">🚨</text><text class="notice-text">信息服务费已耗尽，无法确认接单或联系客户</text><text class="notice-action">去充值 ❯</text></view><view class="section balance-card deposit"><view class="row-between align-center"><view class="balance-meta"><text class="balance-label">货运保证金 (元)</text><text class="balance-value font-bold">{{e}}</text></view><button class="primary-btn recharge-btn-mini" bindtap="{{f}}">充值</button></view><view class="balance-footer"><text>最低限额标准: {{g}}</text><text class="{{['status-tag', 'mini-tag', i]}}">{{h}}</text></view></view><view class="section balance-card info-fee"><view class="row-between align-center"><view class="balance-meta"><text class="balance-label">信息服务费 (元)</text><text class="balance-value font-bold">{{j}}</text></view><button class="primary-btn recharge-btn-mini" bindtap="{{k}}">充值</button></view><view class="balance-footer"><text>按单按次确认扣费, 多充不限</text><text class="{{['status-tag', 'mini-tag', m]}}">{{l}}</text></view></view><view class="section links-section-card"><view class="section-title">资金与消费记录</view><view class="links-list"><view class="link-item" bindtap="{{n}}"><view class="row align-center"><text class="link-icon">💳</text><text class="link-label">在线充值记录</text></view><text class="link-arrow">❯</text></view><view class="link-item" bindtap="{{o}}"><view class="row align-center"><text class="link-icon">📉</text><text class="link-label">订单信息费扣费清单</text></view><text class="link-arrow">❯</text></view><view class="link-item" bindtap="{{p}}"><view class="row align-center"><text class="link-icon">📊</text><text class="link-label">钱包变更账单总流水</text></view><text class="link-arrow">❯</text></view></view></view></view>